{"tid":889802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我都唔想咁:(","createTime":"2018-11-04T22:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T20:01:06.000Z","uid":162818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2885b02c58a2d87cb29ced46dde5759d93dd8bb6","tid":889802,"uid":162818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T22:43:10.000Z","msg":"死唔可以解決問題 但可以逃避所有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有抑鬱症仲去拍拖 累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4a5dd047385c3fca10e5a3b946d84788acb0ce","tid":889802,"uid":62495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T23:55:09.000Z","msg":"逃避完又點<br />\n你屋企人你 朋友你自己都對唔得住<br />\n抑鬱唔係下下拎黎解決任何事的藉口<br />\n唔係因為我抑鬱而要世界上人遷就我<br />\n咁係無可能<br />\n<br />\n當下要做既 就係好好正視番個病<br />\n有病就去食藥睇醫生<br />\n同身邊既人面對面坐低講下自己最內心既感覺 希望同人分擔<br />\n到唔係正經搵個人同你傾吐<br />\n防止自殺係24小時<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而唔係走上黎叫春求安慰<br />\n講自己點慘想死<br />\n咁樣唔會幫到你D咩"},{"pid":"9d90cf1aaaf5c372f8337700eb12b4af2893436f","tid":889802,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T23:57:26.000Z","msg":"你一死 就到你身邊既人承受問題"},{"pid":"651e09c39eacbd1c854d913b2a0406a331e05264","tid":889802,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2885b02c58a2d87cb29ced46dde5759d93dd8bb6","tid":889802,"uid":162818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T22:43:10.000Z","msg":"死唔可以解決問題 但可以逃避所有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有抑鬱症仲去拍拖 累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=HXV2uDpvLWe%2FG6eML%2BiHS0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=797748c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"3a67b5aee9987a7d79b8873eef97077050383b83","tid":889802,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"很抱歉<br />\n接下來要對你做的事<br />\n全是單純的洩憤而已<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/1__ugCxyV7c/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F1__ugCxyV7c%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=caa61468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jHi6T01QCqQ/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjHi6T01QCqQ%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=b9624783&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b583f7ad37f167c3517c63fe89dbdc9d8a54987","tid":889802,"uid":15495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d90cf1aaaf5c372f8337700eb12b4af2893436f","tid":889802,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T23:57:26.000Z","msg":"你一死 就到你身邊既人承受問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"死咗仲有啲咩問題要承受？<br />\n<br />\n爭落財仔，有老婆有仔有女另計"},{"pid":"007d73a2caa7d01eebbdcaaa1cc024fc448e9d78","tid":889802,"uid":190657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T19:59:45.000Z","msg":"Stay strong <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f18cccbfe463bbac1a00e83dcff537e571360e","tid":889802,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T20:01:06.000Z","msg":"拖都冇得拍"}]}